John F. BURTON v. B. R. BAYS, Trustee In Bankruptcy of the ESTATE of The HARBURNEY OIL COMPANY, et al. No. 1501. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Feb. 17, 1937. Ringolsky, Boatright & Jacobs, of Kansas City, Mo., for appellant. L. P. Brooks, of Wichita, Kan., for appellees.

Before LEWIS, PHILLIPS, and BRATTON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeals dismissed on stipulation of the parties.
